text: Hirokazu Higashira (born 7 September 1946) is a Japanese equestrian. He competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Japan Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kyoto
